  </tr>
  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>jQuery is kinda old and also we want to use
<a href="https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-inplaceedit">https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-inplaceedit</a> which requires 1.6.

We use 1.3 on oh-mainline---the current version is 2.0. Clearly we need an
upgrade. It will be great.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
